OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FA mum accused of murdering her own
OL,7,Fbaby has told a jury that her husband
OL,8,Fheadbutted their son and "banged him
OL,9,Fon the bed" within days of him being
OL,10,Fbrought home from hospital.
OL,12,FNivalda Santos Pirjani, 34, and her
OL,13,Fpartner Klevi, 37, are currently on
OL,14,Ftrial at Liverpool Crown Court,
OL,15,Fcharged with the murder of their child
OL,16,FMiguel Pirjani, who died in November
OL,17,F2024.
