OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FThe couple are accused of
OL,7,F"systematically abusing" their 13-week-
OL,8,Fold baby before his death, after he
OL,9,Fwas found to have suffered numerous
OL,10,Fbroken bones and a bleed on the brain.
OL,12,FBoth deny this charge, although the
OL,13,Fmother has admitted causing or
OL,14,Fallowing the death of a child.
OL,16,FEmergency services were called by his
OL,17,Ffather, Klevi, on 24 November 2024,
OL,18,Fwho reported that Miguel was
OL,19,Funresponsive and not breathing.
