OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FServices attended the family home on
OL,7,FPercy Road, Seacombe, Wirral and found
OL,8,Fthe baby in cardiac arrest.
OL,10,FParamedics were able to recover a
OL,11,Fpulse, but he was taken to Alder Hey
OL,12,FChildren's Hospital in an "extremely
OL,13,Fserious" condition.
OL,15,FMiguel remained on life support until
OL,16,F29 November 2024, when he died
OL,17,Ffollowing the removal of artificial
OL,18,Fventilation.
