OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FWhile giving evidence in court on
OL,7,FTuesday 14 October 2025, Pirjani said
OL,8,Fthat her husband had been previously
OL,9,Fviolent to baby Miguel.
OL,11,FNivalda Pirjania recalled that her
OL,12,Fhusband would "get angry" if Miguel
OL,13,Fwas struggling to feed and would
OL,14,F"probably give a slap on Miguel or
OL,15,Fbang his head on Miguel."
OL,17,FMiguel was born on 27 August 2024, and
OL,18,Fspent the first 6 weeks of his life in
OL,19,Fhospital due to medical issues.
