OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FTwo days after the baby was discharged
OL,7,Ffrom his initial stay in hospital,
OL,8,FPirjani said: "Klevi got angry and
OL,9,Flost control and held Miguel by hips
OL,10,Fand banged Miguel on the bed on the
OL,11,Ffloor at lot of times.
OL,13,F"I ran to stop Klevi. Then Klevi left
OL,14,Fand he came back, and he kicked Miguel
OL,15,Fon the left side of his hips."
OL,17,FPirjani said she did not tell anyone
OL,18,Fabout this incident "because she was
OL,19,Fscared of Klevi."
