OL,6,FShe told the court he had been violent
OL,7,Fto her since they moved in together in
OL,8,F2016: "Klevi can be violent,
OL,9,Faggressive, lose control. He (would)
OL,10,Fgive a slap and beat me, on the face
OL,11,Fand on my body."
OL,13,FWhen asked by her counsel Rupert
OL,14,FBowers KC whether she had previously
OL,15,Ftried to leave the relationship, she
OL,16,Fsaid: "Klevi stopped me all the time.
OL,17,FShouting, frightening, scaring me.
