OL,3,CMum accused of murdering baby son says
OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,F"I just tried to run away from the
OL,7,Fhouse. He tried to be aggressive with
OL,8,Fme, lost control, shouting and tried
OL,9,Fto beat me as well."
OL,11,FWhen paramedics were called in
OL,12,FNovember 2024, Nivalda reportedly
OL,13,Fasserted that she did not care for
OL,14,FMiguel. She said Klevi cared for the
OL,15,Fbaby.
OL,17,FProsecutor Peter Wright KC said: "At
OL,18,Fno stage was Nivalda asking for any
OL,19,Fupdates as to Miguel's condition."
