OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FDoctors noted that Miguel had
OL,7,Fsustained bruising on the left side of
OL,8,Fhis head, while a CT scan discovered a
OL,9,Ffissure to his skull and bleeding on
OL,10,Fthe brain, in addition to fractures to
OL,11,Fhis right collarbone, left upper arm
OL,12,Fand left shin.
OL,14,FThe broken bones were said to be of
OL,15,Fvarying age.
