OL,4,C'violent' husband 'lost control'
OL,6,FWright added: "The inevitable
OL,7,Fconclusion to be drawn from the
OL,8,Finjuries was that Miguel had been
OL,9,Fsubjected to a course of conduct in
OL,10,Fwhich serious and obvious injuries had
OL,11,Fbeen sustained.
OL,13,F"We say that Miguel was systematically
OL,14,Fphysically abused by his parents. They
OL,15,Fcaused him really serious non-fatal
OL,16,Finjury with intent so to do. They
OL,17,Fcaused or allowed his death."
